HEADWORD: Loxodromism
<hw>Lox*od"ro*mism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
process of tracing a loxodromic curve; the act of moving as if in a
loxodromic curve.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loxodromy</ent>⟦br⟧
